HEADWORD: Succumb
<hw>Suc*cumb"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Succumbed</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Succumbing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L.
<ets>succumbere</ets>; <ets>sub</ets> under + <ets>cumbere</ets> (in
